  "remarks": "JSC Central Design Bureau of Automatics (TsKBA) is a Russian enterprise which designs and produces components for the Kh-31P missiles, which are used by the Russian Armed Forces in the war of aggression against Ukraine. Therefore, JSC Central Design Bureau of Automatics is supporting materially actions which undermine and threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty and independence of Ukraine. Furthermore, JSC Central Design Bureau of Automatics is also associated with JSC Tactical Missiles Corporation.",
